release.notes:
Store exclusive, explicit cover edition in a gatefold sleeve. 
This release does not feature the track "Judah Smith Interlude" like the other versions of the album.
Includes printed inner sleeves.
Although a few retailers marketed this as 'Limited' the official webstore did not.

Sticker attached to the rear shrink wrap: "Made In Czech Republic".

A Polydor Records Release / An Interscope Records Release in the USA. ℗ & © 2023 Lana Del Rey under exclusive license to Universal Music Operations Limited.
